data.description: BETTER THAN NEW! Charming single story all brick home w/lush landscaping and great curb appeal in the community of Polo Ranch.  Within walking distance to schools, pool, parks, Historic downtown of Fulshear are several eateries and shops. The Leander floor plan is a light and bright open concept, which is great for entertaining. The Living area highlights coffered ceiling & built in speakers. Kitchen boasts quartz counters, island w/sink, abundance of cabinets, stainless steel appliances, pendant lighting & tile. Spacious Primary Bedroom with coffered ceiling & large walk-in closet. The ensuite bath includes dual vanities & tile surround walk-in shower. Nice split floor plan w/built-in bench organizer. 3 large secondary bedrooms. One secondary bedroom ensuite bath with tub/shower, granite counter & decorative mirror. The third full tub-shower bath is accessible to guests. Generator transfer switch installed in garage for quick hook-up & release. Covered patio w/speakers! Sprinklers.
